    "description": "“Tarot For Storytelling” – it's instrument for game designers, writers, screen writers, dungeon masters and other storytellers. It's based on Tarot cards interpritation and various systems of creating stories.<br><br>Now avalible version which has the following plot architectures:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 Card – help you build a connection between two characters or events;<br></li><li> 3 Cards – help you build a connection between three characters or events, as well as build the emphasis of the three acts of your story;<br></li><li> 3 Cards – help you build a connection between four characters or events;<br></li><li> Five Whys - builds a sequence of events that led to this;<br></li><li> Hero Cross – will help you create a full-fledged character of the character with his past, gift, curse, dream and his Shadow.</li></ul><br>I try to release free updates for this app at least once a month.<br><br>In future versions, I plan to add the function of building story chains according to the principles: &quot;Harmon's Circle&quot;, &quot;The Hero's Journey&quot;, as well as add other useful functionality like editing the history window and saving it on your device.",
